text: White Feather is a 1955 American western movie. It was directed by Robert D. Webb. The movie is based on the 1952 story by John Prebble. Actors include Robert Wagner, Debra Paget, Virginia Leith, Hugh O'Brian, John Lund, and Eduard Franz.
